      <title>拜登最新动用赦免权，减免 37 项死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-commutes-37-death-sentences-in-latest-use-of-pardon-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周一减轻 37 名联邦囚犯的死刑，利用其总统赦免权将他们的刑期减为终身监禁，不得假释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-commutes-37-death-sentences-in-latest-use-of-pardon-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登团队将调查中国芯片，为特朗普征收关税埋下伏笔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-team-to-probe-chinese-chips-setting-up-trump-for-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府正在启动一项调查，这将为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提供是否对中国制造的半导体芯片征收新关税的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/biden-team-to-probe-chinese-chips-setting-up-trump-for-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普重拾对格陵兰岛的兴趣，视其为国家安全关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/trump-revives-interest-in-greenland-as-key-to-national-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普暗示他仍然想购买丹麦自治领土格陵兰岛，并称美国对该岛的所有权和控制对于国家安全是“绝对必要的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/trump-revives-interest-in-greenland-as-key-to-national-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 09:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃隆·马斯克为提高效率设定美联储“人员过剩”目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/elon-musk-makes-overstaffed-fed-target-in-quest-for-efficiency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克的重任将从明年 1 月开始让美国政府变得更加高效，而他的目标已经锁定在美联储身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/elon-musk-makes-overstaffed-fed-target-in-quest-for-efficiency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 09:08:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚总理安瓦尔因推动投资而人气飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/malaysian-pm-anwar-approval-ratings-climb-in-latest-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据马来西亚独立中心周一公布的最新民意调查显示，马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣执政两年后，凭借其推动增加投资的支持率升至 54%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/malaysian-pm-anwar-approval-ratings-climb-in-latest-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 08:09:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾警告法律变化可能对预算产生“严重影响”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/taiwan-warns-law-changes-may-have-serious-impacts-on-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾政府表示，预算规则的法律变更可能会导致其 2025 年支出计划脱轨，这凸显出反对派对处于中美紧张关系核心的民主国家新领导人构成的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/taiwan-warns-law-changes-may-have-serious-impacts-on-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 07:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1MDB 向 Amicorp 提出 10 亿美元索赔，以追回资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/1mdb-files-1-billion-claim-against-amicorp-to-recover-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚陷入困境的国家财富基金一马发展有限公司 (1Malaysia Development Bhd.) 已向一家香港企业服务提供商提起 10 亿美元的索赔，以追回其被盗资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/1mdb-files-1-billion-claim-against-amicorp-to-recover-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 07:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马领导人与特朗普就运河控制权展开争执</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/panama-s-leader-takes-up-feud-with-trump-over-canal-s-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马总统拒绝了唐纳德·特朗普关于重新实施美国对巴拿马运河控制的威胁，称其航运通行费并未过高，且该水道的主权不容谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/panama-s-leader-takes-up-feud-with-trump-over-canal-s-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 21:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>总理任期临近，法国期待新政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/france-awaits-new-government-as-the-premier-s-deadline-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁已经没有足够的时间在自己设定的最后期限前任命一个不会被议会的不信任投票轻易推翻的新内阁了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/france-awaits-new-government-as-the-premier-s-deadline-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Dec 2024 20:45:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将总统职位让给马斯克的说法是“骗局”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-22/trump-says-talk-that-he-s-ceded-presidency-to-musk-is-a-hoax</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周日表示，他将成为美国总统——而不是埃隆·马斯克。]]></description>
